item.title: Podcast Repost: NP93 – Street Fighter 25
item.description: Welcome to Nostalgia Pilots! This week, Hugh, Jurd and Spence consider Mobile Fighter G Gundam #30: Beautiful Fighter: Dangerous Allenby! This week, Domon wrecks an arcade machine, Allenby has cold fists, and Rain is totally fine with this. Plus, Argo gets Worfed out of the gate, and the Noble Gundam has strong ribbon game.
